[58.879773, "o", "[Write]\r\n"]
[81.814157, "o", "The text that will be printed is:\r\n\r\n**\"Embossed text\"**\r\n\r\nThis is specified in the gcode file on line 26:\r\n```\r\nM486 AEmbossed text\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe M486 command is a Prusa-specific annotation command that labels objects or layers, and in this case, it indicates that the printer will create embossed text with the content \"Embossed text\" on the existing object.\r\n"]
